    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go! It's got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. Come check it out\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
